{"tid":1433544,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"852郵報：環球時報話警務處處長可委任公安擔任特務警察","createTime":"2019-08-08T13:46:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T13:59:42.000Z","uid":234987,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"578bbbad59ff3c93aa000b322f837f3466121f15","tid":1433544,"uid":234987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:46:12.000Z","msg":"852郵報：<br />\n修訂《逃犯條例》的爭議令香港局勢持續升溫，網上流傳駐港解放軍將介入香港事務，甚至有大陸公安等已混入香港警隊執法。黨媒《環球時報》評論員「補壹刀」昨日在網上發表文章指，香港《公安條例》有條文可容許警務處處長委任公安擔任特務警察，以協助香港警方執行任務。<br />\n<br />\n香港法例245章《公安條例》 ：<br />\n40. 〈行政長官授權他人委任特務警察的權力〉<br />\n行政長官可隨時藉命令授權警務處處長，以書面方式委任任何願意擔任特務警察的人為特務警察，任期由行政長官在該命令中指明。<br />\n<br />\n41.〈特務警察的權力〉<br />\n(1)獲委為特務警察的人，在以該身分行事時所具備的職責、權力、保障及豁免權，均與本條例或任何其他法律所委予或授予警務人員的職責、權力、保障及豁免權相同。<br />\n(2)特務警察須遵從警務處處長向其作出的所有命令。<br />\n(3)本條的規定並不使特務警察有權獲得任何薪酬、退休金或其他報酬。<br />\n<br />\n42.〈特務警察拒絕服從命令〉<br />\n任何特務警察，如無合理辯解而忽略或拒絕服從根據第41(2)條向其發出的有關執行其職責的命令，即屬犯罪，一經循簡易程序定罪，可處第1級罰款及監禁2個月。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/282960/%E3%80%90%E7%A7%BB%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E9%BB%A8%E5%AA%92%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96%E5%93%A1%E5%BC%95%E3%80%8A%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%8B%E3%80%80%E6%8C%87/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F282960%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E5%25AA%2592%25E8%25A9%2595%25E8%25AB%2596%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25BC%2595%25E3%2580%258A%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%258B%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%258C%2587%2F&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9YE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=f7c08965\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/282960/%E3%80%90%E7%A7%BB%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E9%BB%A8%E5%AA%92%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96%E5%93%A1%E5%BC%95%E3%80%8A%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%8B%E3%80%80%E6%8C%87/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap245!zh-Hant-HK?xpid=ID_1438402886106_003\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap245%21zh-Hant-HK%3Fxpid%3DID_1438402886106_003&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9YE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=420a0311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap245!zh-Hant-HK?xpid=ID_1438402886106_003</a>"},{"pid":"a7bc9106b91e305f6a406caebd8a2aaf95b2c92f","tid":1433544,"uid":234987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:47:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"37959ecd0460aafd0b7e8392583c3eee5661dcf6","tid":1433544,"uid":2562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:49:10.000Z","msg":"［緊急］荃灣被斬義士⋯⋯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1433055\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1433055</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有冇文宣幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者設計部手足再改下d圖<br />\n唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/22P5zpN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F22P5zpN.jpg&h=30bad7ac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9RoYUpO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9RoYUpO.png&h=4263cb48&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VFi904O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVFi904O.jpg&h=9a509a22&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L0HVWC9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL0HVWC9.jpg&h=b9ba03e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0OrPgC9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0OrPgC9.png&h=e761163e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yV2ZDRv.jpg\" data-thu